{"id":121,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":121,"title":"D&C 117","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 117"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet, at Far West, Missouri, July 8, 1838, concerning the immediate duties of William Marks, Newel K. Whitney, and Oliver Granger."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.1-9"},"1–9"],", The Lord’s servants should not covet temporal things, for “what is property unto the Lord?”;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.10-16"},"10–16"],", They are to forsake littleness of soul, and their sacrifices will be sacred unto the Lord."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.1","order":"06.05.117.14781"},["b","1"],"Verily thus saith the Lord unto my servant",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"William Marks"],", and also unto my servant Newel K. Whitney, let them settle up their business speedily and journey from the land of Kirtland, before I, the Lord,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"send"],"again the snows upon the earth."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.2","order":"06.05.117.14782"},["b","2"],"Let them awake, and arise, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"come"],"forth, and not tarry, for I, the Lord, command it."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.3","order":"06.05.117.14783"},["b","3"],"Therefore, if they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"tarry"],"it shall not be well with them."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.4","order":"06.05.117.14784"},["b","4"],"Let them repent of all their sins, and of all their covetous desires, before me, saith the Lord; for what is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"property"],"unto me? saith the Lord."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.5","order":"06.05.117.14785"},["b","5"],"Let the properties of Kirtland be turned out for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"debts"],", saith the Lord. Let them go, saith the Lord, and whatsoever remaineth, let it remain in your hands, saith the Lord."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.6","order":"06.05.117.14786"},["b","6"],"For have I not the fowls of heaven, and also the fish of the sea, and the beasts of the mountains? Have I not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"made"],"the earth? Do I not hold the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"destinies"],"of all the armies of the nations of the earth?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.7","order":"06.05.117.14787"},["b","7"],"Therefore, will I not make",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"solitary"],"places to bud and to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"blossom"],", and to bring forth in abundance? saith the Lord."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.8","order":"06.05.117.14788"},["b","8"],"Is there not room enough on the mountains of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Adam-ondi-Ahman"],", and on the plains of Olaha",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"Shinehah"],", or the land where",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"Adam"],"dwelt, that you should covet that which is but the drop, and neglect the more weighty matters?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.9","order":"06.05.117.14789"},["b","9"],"Therefore, come up hither unto the land of my people, even Zion."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.10","order":"06.05.117.14790"},["b","10"],"Let my servant William Marks be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"faithful"],"over a few things, and he shall be a ruler over many. Let him preside in the midst of my people in the city of Far West, and let him be blessed with the blessings of my people."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.11","order":"06.05.117.14791"},["b","11"],"Let my servant Newel K. Whitney be ashamed of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Nicolaitane"],"band and of all their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"secret abominations"],", and of all his littleness of soul before me, saith the Lord, and come up to the land of Adam-ondi-Ahman, and be a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"bishop"],"unto my people, saith the Lord, not in name but in deed, saith the Lord."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.12","order":"06.05.117.14792"},["b","12"],"And again, I say unto you, I remember my servant",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Oliver Granger"],"; behold, verily I say unto him that his name shall be had in sacred remembrance from generation to generation, forever and ever, saith the Lord."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.13","order":"06.05.117.14793"},["b","13"],"Therefore, let him contend earnestly for the redemption of the First Presidency of my Church, saith the Lord; and when he falls he shall rise again, for his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"sacrifice"],"shall be more sacred unto me than his increase, saith the Lord."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.14","order":"06.05.117.14794"},["b","14"],"Therefore, let him come up hither speedily, unto the land of Zion; and in the due time he shall be made a merchant unto my name, saith the Lord, for the benefit of my people."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.15","order":"06.05.117.14795"},["b","15"],"Therefore let no man despise my servant Oliver Granger, but let the blessings of my people be on him forever and ever."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.16","order":"06.05.117.14796"},["b","16"],"And again, verily I say unto you, let all my servants in the land of Kirtland remember the Lord their God, and mine house also, to keep and preserve it holy, and to overthrow the moneychangers in mine own due time, saith the Lord. Even so. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.1a","order":"06.05.117.14797"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.79.79-80"},"D&C 124:79 (79–80)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.1b","order":"06.05.117.14799"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/37.6.5-6"},"Job 37:6 (5–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/148.8"},"Ps. 148:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/11.17.13-17"},"Hel. 11:17 (13–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.24"},"Ether 2:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.2a","order":"06.05.117.14801"},["b","2a"],["span.small","IE"],"from Kirtland."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.3a","order":"06.05.117.14803"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/procrastination"},"Procrastination"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.4a","order":"06.05.117.14805"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/14.4.3-4"},"Mark 14:4 (3–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/104.14"},"D&C 104:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.5a","order":"06.05.117.14807"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.23.22-23"},"D&C 90:23 (22–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.6a","order":"06.05.117.14809"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/creation"},"TG Creation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-works-of"},"God, Works of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-creator"},"Jesus Christ, Creator"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.6b","order":"06.05.117.14811"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.1.1-3"},"Isa. 45:1 (1–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.37"},"1 Ne. 17:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.7a","order":"06.05.117.14813"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/35.1.1-2"},"Isa. 35:1 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.7b","order":"06.05.117.14815"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.24"},"D&C 35:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.13"},"39:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/49.25"},"49:25"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-renewal-of"},"TG Earth, Renewal of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.8a","order":"06.05.117.14817"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/116"},"D&C 116"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.8b","order":"06.05.117.14819"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/3.13"},"Abr. 3:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.8c","order":"06.05.117.14821"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/adam"},"TG Adam"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/eden"},"Eden"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.10a","order":"06.05.117.14823"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/25.23"},"Matt. 25:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.11a","order":"06.05.117.14825"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/2.6.6,15"},"Rev. 2:6 (6, 15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.11b","order":"06.05.117.14827"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/secret-combinations"},"TG Secret Combinations"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.11c","order":"06.05.117.14829"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/72.8.6-8"},"D&C 72:8 (6–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.12a","order":"06.05.117.14831"},["b","12a"],["span.small","IE"],"the agent left by the Prophet to settle his affairs in Kirtland."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/117.13a","order":"06.05.117.14833"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-sacrifice"},"TG Self-Sacrifice"],"."]]}
